reviews.review_text: Warfield Dead - 1980. Show from 1980, not 1989.  Part of the famous 3-set Warfield shows, 1st set being acoustic.  "Greatest Story Ever Told" track made it on "Dead Set" LP.  Nice quality soundboard!
1989? what's time if you're Dead to the core? The space/time continuum paradox
